:02:29.000Z","msg":"真係冇乜用，落幾大雨我都冇用過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9feca0181bbb66857f88a9434e093da06b4e4069","tid":775253,"uid":195215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T09:03:39.000Z","msg":"有嘅落雨個陣屎忽痕咪開下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ce2b7f640dc516aef00eddf4b7a3bdcf3efd327","tid":775253,"uid":9496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T09:18:44.000Z","msg":"咁細架車冇咩所謂"},{"pid":"4818a58f565503be5480e9f06ec13235e81aa166","tid":775253,"uid":57117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T09:20:25.000Z","msg":"好似今朝咁 晒氣前水撥開到最大都濛"},{"pid":"825573323356dae6066701d4a45786fed90bbe03","tid":775253,"uid":83032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T09:24:40.000Z","msg":"淘寶有得淘番個水潑臂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都有用架如果真係好撚大雨果陣<br />\n凡係有水尾潑嘅車都係因為車尾係真空區 啲風吹唔走啲雨所以先要加水潑 安全來說我覺得都需要裝嘅 如果落好大有時都會睇唔到後車距離"},{"pid":"6286d9111c367c8138a492bf9d5e1dfcfe6bedbb","tid":775253,"uid":116203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T09:37:32.000Z","msg":"試過見到冇雨但前面架車開左後水撥個制，重點係佢得個摇臂冇裝到水撥，所以佢完全唔會見到係開左，勁搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"394153f9af74f02e86e99c4f5ec11aa24d95d4d0","tid":775253,"uid":86088,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T09:46:30.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打們解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 如果淘水潑，係咪有得再叫車房架番，因為架車好似連水撥個粒野都係無的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c899f618e16747e55a10b47f239034a4048071b0","tid":775253,"uid":83032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"394153f9af74f02e86e99c4f5ec11aa2